lead_paragraph: Brandon Stone won the South African Open on Sunday for his maiden European Tour title, becoming the youngest player to win the event since it joined the tour schedule in 1997.

headline.print_headline: Brandon Stone Claims Maiden Euro Tour Win at SA Open
